      71.99,
      95.19,
      452.71,
      127.45
    ],
    "text": "1) Read the passage about Kanneliya and say whether the following statements are true (T) or false (F).",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      145.28,
      446.99,
      229.46
    ],
    "text": "1. Kanneliya is the one and only forest reserve in Sri Lanka. \u25a1 2. There is a variety of wildlife in the Kanneliya Forest Reserve. \u25a13. March is a good time to visit Kanneliya to see the waterfalls. \u25a14. Deforestation has affected the water levels of the streams. \u25a15. Hiking is difficult in the month of June. \u25a1",
    "fonts": [
      "SimSun",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      247.29,
      449.98,
      314.47
    ],
    "text": "2) Which of the following is the main idea of this passage? \u2022 There are many places of natural beauty like Kanneliya in Sri Lanka. \u2022 Kanneliya is an ideal destination for nature lovers. \u2022 Kanneliya cannot be visited throughout the year due to climatic conditions.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      97.69,
      361.43,
      153.19,
      377.6
    ],
    "text": "Activity 04",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-BoldItalic",
