      71.99,
      369.44,
      452.69,
      416.81
    ],
    "text": "ListeningListen to the dialogue and fill in the gaps. Then report to the class details about the annual trip of Gemunu Maha Vidyalaya.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      429.44,
      450.8,
      546.41
    ],
    "text": "1. The students of Gemunu Maha Vidyalaya visited \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026......... (Nilaweli, Pasdikuda).2. It is in the \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026 (Batticaloa, Mannar) District.3. It is \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026. (218, 288) km away from Colombo.4. It is very important as a place of \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026(historical value, tourist attraction).5. The students were fascinated by the beauty of the \u2026\u2026...\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026 (jungle, beach).",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
