      105.25
    ],
    "text": "Reading and Writing",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      117.88,
      453.02,
      191.65
    ],
    "text": "The students of Gemunu Maha Vidyalaya are planning to hold a poster competition on the theme \u201cLet\u2019s Recycle Our Waste\u201d. This is the announcement they have prepared to inform the students of the competition. Read it aloud. Next write a note to your friend who is absent from school informing him/ her about the competition.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      224.34,
      243.8,
      297.66,
      259.96
    ],
    "text": "Announcement",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      129.38,
      272.6,
      395.58,
      389.56
    ],
    "text": "The Environmental Society of Gemunu Maha Vidyalaya has organized a poster competition on the theme \u201cLet\u2019s Recycle Our Waste\u201d to mark the Earth Day. The competition will be held on 5th June 2013 from 8 a.m onwards at the Main Hall of the school. Students from grade 6 to 13 can take part in the competition. More details will be displayed on the Environmental Society noticeboard.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      71.97,
      417.64,
      256.95,
      433.81
    ],
    "text": "Now do activity 07 of your workbook.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      97.69,
      445.95,
      153.19,
      462.12
    ],
    "text": "Activity 08",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-BoldItalic",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      476.21,
      116.66,
      492.37
    ],
    "text": "Speaking",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      501.51,
      452.71,
      588.77
    ],
    "text": "The teacher will divide the class into two groups. Each group should find information for and against the following topic:\u201cUsing traditional methods is better than using modern technology in agriculture.\u201dSelect students to represent your group and have a class debate on the above topic.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      597.91,
      256.19,
      613.16
    ],
    "text": "Here are some guidelines to help you:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      628.06,
      445.67,
      652.76
    ],
    "text": "97For free distribution",
    "fonts": [
      "Cambria-Italic",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      49.65,
      453.01,
      192.0
    ],
    "text": "Moderator:Ladies and gentlemen! We welcome you all. The topic of today\u2019s debate is \u201c\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026...\u201d Let me introduce our two debating teams. On my right we have the proposing team who will speak for the topic. On my left we have the opposing team who will oppose the proposition team\u2019s point of view.Now please welcome the leader of the proposing team.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      229.65,
      378.45,
      246.0
    ],
    "text": "Useful language expressions for presenting your arguments:",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      249.84,
      233.34,
      266.01
    ],
    "text": "It is obvious that ............",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      269.85,
      225.49,
      286.01
    ],
    "text": "To begin with\u2026\u2026\u2026",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      289.85,
      182.35,
      306.02
    ],
    "text": "We believe that \u2026\u2026...",
    "fonts": [
